00:00:28.580 --> 00:00:42.282
They are dressed in African garb with tribal beads. There is red on these outfits and they have headdresses on.

00:00:42.283 --> 00:00:50.699
As they are looking toward the sun, I see a new oil running down their faces, and there is a glory on them.

00:00:50.700 --> 00:01:04.988
There is nothing around but dirt and these heights, but as this glory is falling, oil is saturating them.

00:01:04.989 --> 00:01:16.634
It is like whenever you dump oil, it spreads, and the glory of the Lord is coming upon the African people.

00:01:16.635 --> 00:01:31.831
