00:02:28.399 --> 00:02:36.958
A wave will come and pull, and another wave will come right on the heels of the creative miracles.

00:02:36.959 --> 00:02:51.033
You are about to see a wave of the glory upon this world. It will come in waves; it will look like one is receding, but another wave will come.

00:02:51.034 --> 00:03:07.516
